{"lemma":"صُحْبَةٌ","slug":"صُحْبَةٌ","root":"ص.ح.ب","root_slug":"ص-ح-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/ص-ح-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n23780"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B5%D9%8F%D8%AD%D9%92%D8%A8%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"companions; collective of صَاحِب (ṣāḥib)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of صَحِبَ (ṣaḥiba) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"companionship, fellowship"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/sˤuħ.ba/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n23780","headword_ar":"صُحْبَةٌ","root":"SHb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"an inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaHibahu","text_ar":"صَحِبَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]. (S, A, Msb, K, &c.) ―         -b2-  [As a simple subst.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Companionship."},{"kind":"text","text":"Hence,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lahu SuHobapN","text_ar":"لَهُ صُحْبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", often occurring in biographies as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He had companionship"},{"kind":"text","text":"with the Prophet; i. e. he was one of the Companions of the Prophet. And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xarajotu SuHobapa Alr~asuwli","text_ar":"خَرَجْتُ صُحْبَةَ الرَّسُولِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", frequently occurring in trads., meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I went forth in the companionship of the Apostle,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in company with the Apostle."},{"kind":"text","text":"Hence also] one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hamalotu AlkitaAba","text_ar":"حَمَلْتُ الكِتَابَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SuHobatiY","text_ar":"صُحْبَتِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I carried the book with me"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Msb.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SuHobapu Als~afiynapi","text_ar":"صُحْبَةُ السَّفِينَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The companionship of the ship"},{"kind":"text","text":"] is a post-classical phrase, denoting, by way of comparison, that which has no permanence. (Har p. 258.) ―         -b3-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaAHibN","text_ar":"صَاحِبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", of which it is a quasipl. n."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}